## Shared Protocol

- User instructions override skill defaults.
- Report workflow status with exactly one of: `DONE`, `DONE_WITH_CONCERNS`, `BLOCKED`, `NEEDS_CONTEXT`.
- Escalate instead of guessing when requirements are missing, correctness is uncertain, or scope exceeds what can be verified.
- Process skills come before implementation skills.
- When the task touches money movement, balances, settlement, limits, reconciliation, or regulated audit trails, apply financial-grade controls instead of convenience shortcuts.

